result.name: Hong Kong Tastes

reviews.text:
Good environment and tasty food 
I visit them for many times with family.  The price is also reasonable and acceptable around $50~100. I really enjoy their burger which is full with cheese, a egg and beef. It is good to try.
Tea set, so good!

ordered the sea eel rice. fish is not fresh, a bit stinky. Milk tea is okay. 

Staff service is Poor. not recommend to go twice.

Since 1956, this HK style canteen was here to serve. No significant food or drinks to intro., may be bottle of milk teat does. If you are fans of HK style. You may give a try. Before they renovated, it was a good place for shooting HK drama and movie here. Come and try.

Milk tea is milky smooth, yummy. French toast with hazelnut jam is yummy.  Hainanese Chicken Rice chicken is tender and it's chilli sauce is tasty too. The pineapple bun with butter is so so can do without.

result.adr_address: 香港深水埗青山道62號D
result.name: 雪山冰廳

reviews.text: 食物質素👍
必到的選擇👍👍👍👍👍

今天下班經過冰室，因肚餓，先內進吃小許東西，之後還豎等另一半，便叫她過來一起吃。

避風塘炸脾 $28✱
皮酥脆不肥膩，肉軟有味，咬到蒜粒更香脆。

檳城叻沙摻摻餐 $50
湯底稠度還可以，有鮮蝦味，蝦彈牙，魚，豆卜， 油麵煙韌彈牙，米粉爽腍，惟獨欠了芽菜，味道ok。
日本櫻花蝦炒蛋配牛乳厚多士
滑蛋配煙韌鮮味櫻花蝦，頗有趣，牛油麵包焗得很鬆香，好味。
熱檸蜜 $9 跟餐
甜酸度剛好，因檸檬白色皮會有澀味，拮完檸檬便把他拿起，這杯被我調得頗好飲。

芝士焗龍波士頓龍蝦海鮮飯 $108✨
濃香芝士，白汁足夠，海鮮頗多，鮮甜龍蝦半隻，魷魚，青口，蟹柳，魚片，仿鮑片，用三色椒與蛋做炒飯底， 好味 。
華田曲奇妙趣 $19
加了忌廉，彩色粒粒與曲奇妙趣餅乾， 華田飲落滑溜少甜， ok。

Good environment and tasty food 
I visit them for many times with family.  The price is also reasonable and acceptable around $50~100. I really enjoy their burger which is full with cheese, a egg and beef. It is good to try.
朋友介紹來的，走的滿頭大汗，不過很值得喔！波蘿油麵包很好吃😋，還夾個半熟蛋跟cheese 片，很合我胃口，好吃！瓶裝奶茶跟咖啡不甜，很濃郁。用餐環境乾淨，服務也不錯，是間老店！👍
